Input elements - attributes, properties, etc..
- 22 to 23 input elements in HTML.

reset -
Shortcut - input:reset

E.g. - default value show using reset
	<label for="fname">First Name</label>
            <input type="text" placeholder="first name" value="swapnil" id="fname">
            <input type="reset" value="reset">
            <button type="submit">Submit</button>
			
multiple values in select -
E.g. -
	<select name="editors" id="" multiple>
                  <option value="vscode">vscode</option>
                  <option value="sublime">sublime</option>
  </select>
	
	
Rare use of datalist in HTML -
- very complex form element
- all same that the select.
- very confusing.. not used anyone.

E.g. -

<input list="editors" name="editors">
            <datalist id="editors">
                  <option value="vscode">vscode</option>
                  <option value="sublime">sublime</option>
            </datalist>
			


